# 📦 TechStore - Full Stack E-Commerce Platform

A full-stack e-commerce web application built using **React**, **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB**, fully containerized with **Docker** and deployed on an **AWS EC2 instance** using **NGINX** as a reverse proxy.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

> *(Add your EC2 public IP or domain here)*  
Example: http://your-ec2-ip

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React (Vite)
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- NGINX (for serving build)

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- JWT Authentication

### Database
- MongoDB

### DevOps / Deployment
- Docker
- Docker Compose
- AWS EC2
- NGINX Reverse Proxy

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 User authentication (Login/Register)
- 🛍️ Product listing
- 🛒 Shopping cart functionality
- 📦 REST API backend
- ⚡ Fast React frontend
- 🐳 Fully containerized setup
- ☁️ Deployed on AWS EC2

---

## 🐳 Project Architecture

```text
Client (Browser)
      ↓
   NGINX
      ↓
React Frontend (Container)
      ↓
Node.js Backend (Container)
      ↓
MongoDB (Container)